{"id":199556,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/12/global-voices-南非：科幻小说《城市是座动物园》即将改拍/","date":"2011-12-02T15:01:16Z","modified":"2011-12-02T15:01:16Z","title":"Global Voices | 南非：科幻小说《城市是座动物园》即将改拍电影","content":"<p><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/south-african-sci-fi-novelist-lauren-beukes-zoo-city-to-get-film-adaptation\" href=\"http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/south-african-sci-fi-novelist-lauren-beukes-zoo-city-to-get-film-adaptation\">南非的科幻小说《城市是座动物园》（<em>Zoo City</em>）</a>即将搬上大银幕：“南非作家萝伦．别克斯（Lauren Beukes）的科幻小说《城市是座动物园》，不仅拿下多项文学奖项，亦以其巧妙的独创性赢得全球佳评，日前小说的电影版权授予了同样出身南非的制片人海伦娜．史普宁（Helena Spring，其作品包括了<em>Dust</em>、<em>Yesterday</em>与<em>The First Grader</em>）。”</p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/ndesanjo-macha/\" title=\"文章导读 Ndesanjo Macha\">Ndesanjo Macha</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/shanta/\" title=\"文章导读 Shanta\">Shanta</a></span></span><br />\n · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/11/30/south-africa-sci-fi-novel-zoo-city-to-get-film-adaptation/\" title=\"阅读原文  [en]\">阅读原文  [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/12/02/10163/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E%EF%BC%9A%E7%A7%91%E5%B9%BB%E5%B0%8F%E8%AF%B4%E3%80%8A%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%98%AF%E5%BA%A7%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E5%9B%AD%E3%80%8B%E5%8D%B3%E5%B0%86%E6%94%B9%E6%8B%8D%E7%94%B5%E5%BD%B1&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F02%2F10163%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F12%2F02%2F10163%2F&#038;desc=%E5%8D%97%E9%9D%9E%EF%BC%9A%E7%A